Defective planetary gears.

00:01:46.333 --> 00:01:47.900
Yeah, you have planetary
gears, where you have

00:01:47.900 --> 00:01:49.533
a sun gear and planet gears.

00:01:49.533 --> 00:01:50.633
I didn't know
anything about it.

